Henry Roussel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_Roussel 0 Henry Roussel (1875–1946), also known as Henry Roussell, was a French silent film actor, film director and screenwriter best known for his silent films of the 1910s and 1920s. He starred in well over 40 films between 1912 and 1939.
